abstract: Mr. Dulos had been in critical condition after suffering carbon monoxide poisoning on Tuesday, in an apparent suicide attempt.
lead_paragraph: Fotis Dulos, the Connecticut man accused of murdering his estranged wife, Jennifer Dulos, last May in a case that received national attention, died on Thursday, his lawyer said, two days after he attempted suicide at his home.
